00:08:31.530 --> 00:08:32.830
Goo Joon Pyo.

00:08:33.100 --> 00:08:34.420
Jan Di.

00:09:31.130 --> 00:09:33.050
¿Por cuánto tiempo vas a llorar?

00:09:33.520 --> 00:09:34.630
Si alguien te viera...

00:09:34.750 --> 00:09:36.710
